<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l12"><expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan . vnd dıe ſache <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd eẅr . <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
