<ab facs="#facs_205_r1l14">ſo well <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von wertheim / ʒu <expan>eıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntlıche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag </ab>
