<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, es ist unser <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan cert="unknown">F<ex>ricz</ex></expan>
<expan>Tandorff<ex>er</ex></expan> mit <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> graf <expan>Joh<ex>an</ex></expan> von
                        Wertheim <expan>gelawbbr<ex>ief</ex></expan> auf disz zeit zu uns
                                <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> und hat darauf
                                <expan>geworbe<ex>n</ex></expan>, als wir
                            <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Wertheim vormals
                                <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> getan und die sache
                                <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> und ewr <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu
                                <expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>tage<ex>n</ex></expan> bracht <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also
                        sey uns das ein <expan>gefalle<ex>n</ex></expan>, so well
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> von Wertheim zu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntliche<ex>n</ex></expan> tag gen ewch
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> zu uns gen
                            <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, von <app>
<note><q type="date">nu sunntag schierist über viii
                                tag</q>17.11.1420</note>
</app> zu nacht bey uns zu sein und des morgens am montag darnach zu den
                                <expan>teyding<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>greiffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, das <expan>verkünd<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>, was ewr <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        darinn sein welle, daz ir uns das bey disem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> lasset, daz wir
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Denn wo
                        wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
